name: First Circle of Chaos
effect:
When this card is activated: Add 1 Spell/Trap that mentions "Dark Magician" or "Magician of Black Chaos" from your Deck or GY to your hand. Spell/Trap Cards you control that mention "Dark Magician" or "Magician of Black Chaos" are unaffected by your opponent’s cards or effects.
You can only activate 1 "First Circle of Chaos" per turn.
